                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
                    <h3>MAP (Members Attending Parliament) </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    MAP tracks the attendance of Indian MPs in Lok Sabha (lower house).
                    <p>
                       Currently data for 15th Lok Sabha is presented. Data for 12 sessions has been included.
                       <h3>Idea</h3>
                       Conceptualized this idea, thanks to a <a href="https://twitter.com/binaryfootprint/status/314445030242787328">Tweet</a>.
                       <h3> Data </h3>
                       Data has been accessed from <a href="http://164.100.47.132/members_attendance/mainscreen.aspx"> Lok Sabha website</a>.
                       Data is <a href="data/">available</a> in CSV format. Data can <i>potentially</i> be corrupted at few places. Please report to <a href="https://twitter.com/bkamapantula">@bkamapantula</a>.
                       <h4>Data format</h4>
                       Id, MP Name, Number of days signed, Number of days missed, Gender, State, Party, Constituency
                       <h3> Code </h3>
                       Code for parsing the data out of the Lok Sabha website will be made available soon.
                       To contribute, head to <a href="https://github.com/bkamapantula/MPAttendance">Github</a>.
                       <h3>To-do</h3>
                       <ul>
                           <li> State-wise MP attendance </li>
                           <li> Day-wise MP attendance </li>
                       </ul>
                    </p>
                </div> 
